      "rationale": "Five operating points (2–6 L/min, 2000–3500 RPM) replicated from FDA benchmark dataset. Fluid temperature, viscosity, and hematocrit documented with ±2% measurement uncertainty. Simulation inlet conditions matched to within 1% of experimental values."
