    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors were scoped to not-assessed status consistent with MRL 2 requirements. NIH predictions fall within 20% of experimental measurements across the full operating envelope. The computational model is accepted as sufficiently credible to identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. This assessment has been applied to support clinical research submissions and internal design optimization workflows.",
